posting_body: ['Contact Information:', 'show contact info', 'Rose Mall Apartments | Hornig Companies |', '2200  Pascal St Apt 201, Roseville, MN 55113', 'DESCRIPTION-  $1 Month Rent Free W/ 12 Month Lease & Move in by 9/1!', '______________________________________', 'Come home to the quiet, convenience of Rose Mall Apartments!', 'Find us across the street from Har-Mar Shopping Center and Super Target in the heart of Roseville, just off Highway 36.', 'Our community features spacious 1 (880 sq. ft.) and 2 (1,000 sq. ft.) bedroom floor plans - many with a private balcony.', 'The classic buildings are designed around tranquil center courtyards!', 'Our community also offers private, detached garages, non-smoking buildings, laundry rooms on every floor, an outdoor pool, and gas BBQ grills with picnic areas.', 'Rose Mall Apartments - where home is.', 'Call us today to schedule a tour of your new home!', 'RENTAL FEATURES', '________________________________________', '•\tLiving room', '•\tDining room', '•\tWalk-in closet', '•\tStove / Oven', '•\tRefrigerator', '•\tDishwasher', '•\t2 Air Conditioners', '•\tCable-ready', '•\tPet-free community', 'COMMUNITY FEATURES', '________________________________________', '•\tOnline application', '•\tOnline Rent Payment Portal', '•\tControlled access', '•\tOutdoor pool', '•\tBarbecue area', '•\tOff-street parking', '•\tOn-site management', '•\tOn-site maintenance', '•\t24-hour emergency maintenance', 'DETAILS', '________________________________________', '•\tRent: $1,300.00', '•\tApplication Fee: $45.00', '•\tSecurity Deposit: $400.00', '•\t12 Month Lease', '•\t6 and 9-month leases are available for an additional fee.', 'Contact the office for details.', 'Office Hours', '________________________________________', 'Monday-Thursday 10:00 am - 5:30 pm', 'Friday 10:00 am - 5:00 pm', 'Saturday 10:00 am - 2:00 pm', 'More information and application at <URL>']
